com.empatica.empalink.delegate

Interface EmpaDataDelegate


  • public interface EmpaDataDelegate
    The EmpaDataDelegate interface defines methods for receiving data from an Empatica device. All timestamps are Unix Time in seconds.

        void didReceiveIBI(float ibi,
                   double timestamp)
        This method is invoked when a new interbeat interval (IBI) value is available. You can compute the heart rate as (60 / ibi).
        Parameters:
        ibi - an IBI value
        timestamp - the timestamp for the IBI value
